text: When you're unemployed, you come out of the gym more tired than you went in. But when you're employed, you go to the gym completely exhausted and actually come out more energized afterwards. You live in the upside down now. Nothing makes sense anymore. All the rules are off.

If "Chicken on a Raft" was written today, instead of "I ought to be 'flogging' in a feather bed", the lyrics would probably go "I ought to be 'GOONING' in a feather bed". Goes to show what state the world has come to now...
